<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1455812>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–4. Efferia alia sp. nov. Male terminalia: 1. Intact, left side; 2. Gonostylus; 3. Phallus; and 4. Aedeagus with tubes and phallic flange. Abbreviations: aedeagus with tubes= aed; apical process of epandrium=ap; epandrium=epan; epandrial notch=epnh; gonocoxite=gncx; phallic flange=fla; pygidium=pyg; sternite 9 =st9." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1455812/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

